nt||sk||at|bseagram:  Declare's job is now to count winners
Winners are SURE tricks that will win WITHOUT losing the lead
Guaranteed tricks
Fast tricks
NO ACE, NO winner!
e.g. If you have KQJ10 in a suit, you have ZERO winners|
