nt||at|bseagram:  We count losers in SUIT contracts and winners in NT contracts
So clubs is the project suit
You see, I believe that NT's are easier contracts than suit contracts because in suit contracts we also have a project suit but we have one additional decision to make at start of hand
That is: DO I PULL TRUMP FIRST OR NOT???
In No Trump, that decision is removed.    So project suit first|
